cturaldigest.com/story/best-brooklinen-sheets\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ereports\u003c/a\u003e that in addition to its luxurious sheen, it’s “super classic, smooth, and has a crisp feel.”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"a-statement-bed-frame\" tabindex=\"-1\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eA Statement Bed Frame\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://cna.st/p/39ZGmWZ6fEZzHhxQ4MThfhFVX4sBdzyzV5znitv6hpcJzA3zMLcnxszvXNBsTp9P67QBiFwiv1qv7wFJMtWuKYsjk6umHATS7ruXy8oSeXz9dwDK67XGbyW8yC3Ymy5Rz1KUAKRyWjUmonpdRQx6Co95RBExLgwDSbgG1JEguswDEcFyYoCdK31U9m2rRWSfb6UNmDtMZR2FXSQjhdx2aUgMsra8ghjjvb9khVQWny3yCdEmg9Rzgqz4CCEZNcZKoYSggvia2kKykpqVtviDg3p\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener sponsored\" tabindex=\"-1\" data-offer-url=\"https://www.serenaandlily.com/products/franklin-four-poster-bed/461249\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Serena \u0026amp; Lily Franklin Four Poster Bed\" src=\"https://media.architecturaldigest.com/photos/67c208b19672a4241bee67c0/3:4/w_748%2Cc_limit/AD%2520Product%2520Image%2520(22).png\" srcset=\"https://media.architecturaldigest.com/photos/67c208b19672a4241bee67c0/3:4/w_120,c_limit/AD%20Product%20Image%20(22).png 120w, https://media.architecturaldigest.com/photos/67c208b19672a4241bee67c0/3:4/w_240,c_limit/AD%20Product%20Image%20(22).png 240w, https://media.architecturaldigest.com/photos/67c208b19672a4241bee67c0/3:4/w_320,c_limit/AD%20Product%20Image%20(22).png 320w, https://media.architecturaldigest.com/photos/67c208b19672a4241bee67c0/3:4/w_640,c_limit/AD%20Product%20Image%20(22).png 640w\" sizes=\"100vw\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"upc_undefined\" type=\"embed\"\u003eSerena \u0026amp; Lily Franklin Four Poster Bed\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e“Pieces like four-poster beds, commodes, and slipper chairs add a sense of tradition,